Finnish Apr trade surplus rose to FIM 4 . 3 bln - NCB . Finland ' s trade surplus rose to 4 . 28 billion markka in April from 3 . 47 billion in March and from 3 . 77 billion in April last year , the National Customs Board ( NCB ) said in statement on Wednesday . The NCB earlier reported premilinary April trade surplus at 4 . 0 billion markka . The value of exports rose 16 . 0 percent year - on - year in April and the value of imports also rose 16 . 0 percent , NCB said . Trade balance ( million markka ) : April ' 97 Mar ' 97 April ' 96 Exports 18 , 207 16 , 043 15 , 759 Imports 13 , 925 12 , 575 11 , 987 Balance + 4 , 282 + 3 , 468 + 3 , 772 - - Helsinki newsroom + 358 - 9 - 680 50 245 , news @ reuters . fi 
